rows.label: tev040101_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Auld about the Prone's way of life.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Auld if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0001
rows.name:
Prone are one with beasts. Prone feed on beast to live.
Then Prone die to feed beast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0002
rows.name: I also will give my flesh to beast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0003
rows.name:
*cough* Do you see, Earth alien? Prone obey laws
of nature. Return to nature when time comes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0004
rows.name:
This must sound odd to Earth aliens.
You cling to life with all your strength.
Even live in mechanical bodies to avoid it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0005
rows.name:
This seems unnatural to me. *cough*
I do not understand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0010
rows.name: *cough* My body fails. My time is short.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0011
rows.name:
But I do not... *cough* I do not fear end.
Nature calls me home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0012
rows.name:
My grandson Nemard will grow strong.
Then I will feed beast with no regrets.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG0013
rows.name:
But he is not ready. Not to be warrior. Or father.
Mira will chew him up if he is not stronger.
I cannot rest knowing this. *cough*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG1001
rows.name: Unnnh... My body fails me... *cough* But still...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG1002
rows.name:
My mind is at peace. Nemard has finally found mate.
He can stand tall.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG1003
rows.name: I can leave family in his hands. I am ready to die.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040101_MSG1004
rows.name:
It is good. *cough* I have no regrets.
May my flesh nourish beasts of this world![ST:wait ]
